text: Politotdel () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Dmitriyevskoye Rural Settlement of Koshekhablsky District, Adygea, Russia. The population was 230 as of 2018. There are 4 streets. == Ethnicity == The khutor is inhabited by Tatars. == References == Category:Rural localities in Koshekhablsky District
title: Politotdel, Republic of Adygea
